==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: wù yĭ è xiăo ér wéi zhī
===Etymology===
a quote from the ''[[w:Romance of the Three Kingdoms|Romance of the Three Kingdoms]]''

===Proverbs===
'''[[勿]][[以]][[惡]][[小]][[而]][[為]][[之]]'''
# Do not commit an evil act just because it is small in scale.
===Alternate forms===
[[勿以恶小而为之]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[勿以善小而不為]]

